channel.title: Pbscape Development
channel.description:
[center][b] [img]http://www.pbscape.net/download/file.php?logo=forum_logo.png[/img] Hello guys, This is Pbscpe, I have been working on this source for a good Three Months and tbh I think I did good. If you want to contact me about the server, Heres my contact info. Plus YouTube video below![/b][/center] [center][b]Application: [code] Can you code Java, HTML, or BB code: Position: Experience (Scale 1-10): Age: Time you will use a day on the server: Have you had this position in another server: MSN: [/code]
[center][b]Info to contact me: MSN Is my main instant messenger to talk to you MSN: Pblord7@sinzscape.net EMAIL: Pblord7@sinzscape.net [/b][/center]
[center][b]I am currently hosting my server 24/7, I will list some of the things I have done.
Fully working PVP Shop and Pk Point System. Donor Point System and Donor Point Shop. Fully working new currency for staff (A new twist on staff shops since there only able to option by spawning), with working read opition. Fully working custom minigame called Souls. You go into the portal and kill the monster for points. Fun pk is Castle Wars. (You get team capes theres just no taking flags) Most specs and animations are correct. Custom bosses, they hit high and are somewhat hard to kill. Fully working Dual Arena, No staking. Full working Fight Pits and Jad Minigame. Custom High-scores that are in the game. If your staff your crown is red (only on your client) so you know what you said since it doesn't blend in
[center][b]I have been working on this server for a good 3 Months and its finally starting to workout nice.
